hong kong februari trade swing into deficit hong kong record a 3.51 billion h.k . dlr deficit in februari after a 2.54 billion dlr surplu in januari as import climb and export slid , the censu and statist depart said . the deficit compar with a deficit of 1.76 billion dlr in februari 1986. import rose to 24.12 billion dlr , up 2.6 pct from januari 's 23.52 billion dlr and 42 pct abov the 16.98 billion dlr record in februari 1986. total export for the month fell 20.9 pct to 20.61 billion dlr from 26.06 billion in januari . februari export were still 35.4 pct abov the 15.22 billion dlr record in the same month last year . re-export , the territori 's tradit entrepot trade , outpac domest produc export for the first time sinc march 1985. re-export fell 11.6 pct to 10.62 billion dlr from 12.0 billion dlr in januari but were 54 pct abov februari 1986 ' 6.88 billion dlr . domest export slid 28.9 pct to 9.99 billion dlr from januari 's 14.05 billion dlr but were up 19.7 pct over the 8.35 billion dlr record in februari 1986 .